            </titleStmt>
            <publicationStmt>
                <p>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org<seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-03-27T20:42:41.904+09:00"> PING</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:02:17.579+09:00">the man bribed Bó Lǐxī using five sheep skins</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:03:10.905+09:00">and made him conduct a carriage to go to Qín (in order to deliver the salt).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:03:58.492+09:00">When Duke Mù of Qín was checking the salt</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:05:40.31+09:00">he noticed that Bó Lǐxī's oxen looked feisty,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:04:28.64+09:00">and he said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:05:00.323+09:00">"The load is heavy, and it is a long way so there is danger,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:05:55.994+09:00">Bó Lǐxī replied:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:06:17.091+09:00">"I've been feeding them in time</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:14:27.112+09:00">and I've been deploying them without recklessness.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:08:32.431+09:00">When there was danger</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:08:36.435+09:00"> I personally protected them from in front and from behind,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:08:51.968+09:00">so that is why they look so feisty."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:10:02.709+09:00">Duke Mù of Qín understood that Bó Lǐxī was a true gentleman.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:11:40.924+09:00">He ordered officials to provide for a bath (for Bó Lǐxī) gave him new garments and a new hat, and he sat down together with him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:13:20.249+09:00">The Duke was greatly pleased with Bó Lǐxī.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:13:02.946+09:00">Some days later, when discussing matters of administration with Gōngsūn Zhī,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-16a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-04-02T18:43:42.759+09:00">Ich hab das jetzt mal saubergemacht.</seg>
                </p>
